summary: I choose ewe! One reason I like sheep is that they are associated with lesbians because of how common lesbian sheep are and the...
caption: I choose ewe! One reason I like sheep is that they are associated with lesbians because of how common lesbian sheep are and the studies about them including the popular “Lesbian Sheep Syndrome”. I think the same thing is true in the Pokemon world! c: I am hoping shiny Wooloo will either be pink, a cotton candy blue, or a black sheep to match with Mareep in different ways. Happy Pride!
